{"tid":1024111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網絡專家：用 RTX2080 Ti 破解 Windows 八位密碼只需 2.5 小時","createTime":"2019-02-16T09:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T03:57:46.000Z","uid":105678,"like":113,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"9e85ad3083e1a50481c4f5f17f957d9f8777e496","tid":1024111,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"曾做過黑客的網絡保安專家 Tinker 在最新一份報告中指出，使用 NVIDIA 最新圖像處理器 GeForce RTX 2080 Ti 結合開源密碼軟件，在 2.5 小時內就能破解 8 位數字的 Windows 密碼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2019-02-16-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885.36.05-768x453.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2019-02-16-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25885.36.05-768x453.png&h=cf943f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 2011 年網絡保安研究員 Steven Myer 曾警告，用「蠻力攻擊」（brute force attack）方式只需 44 天就能破解 Windows 上 8 位元的密碼。而 4 年後的 2015 年，軟件開發者 Jeff Atwood 亦曾警告用戶密碼的平均長度是 8 位文字，表示眾多用戶對於加長密碼的意願沒有加強。<br />\n<br />\n如今網絡保安專家 Tinker 表示，使用開源破解軟件「hashcat 6.0.0」再配合 GeForce RTX 2080 Ti 圖像處理器，在 2.5 小時內就能破解 8 位密碼。這位專家表示，對於現今的先進硬件與軟件來說，8 位密碼對於一台電腦基本上毫無意義。<br />\n<br />\n開源軟件「hashcat」的「蠻力攻擊」方式對於使用 NTLM 驗證方式的 Windows 以及 使用 Active Directory 的主機特別有效。雖然現在 Windows 已經使用了 Kerberos 方式驗證密碼，但它在本機儲存密碼，以及使用 Active Directory 網域控制器的資料庫儲存密碼時，仍使用 NTLM 驗證方式。<br />\n<br />\nTinker 同時表示，人們使用大階、小階英文字、數字、記號等令到密碼更加複雜，只會令到我們記憶密碼更加困難。而早前亦有網絡專家表示，複雜的密碼並無實際意義。Tinker 提醒用戶，比起「Lm7xR0w」這個 8 位文字密碼，「phonecoffeesilverrisebaseball」這 5 個單詞混合而成的密碼更難被破解。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：The Register"},{"pid":"5a2230ced809cb681649b115b7413eb2586f6df6","tid":1024111,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5487b0cce96280f099aa8419e52c0b595992210e","tid":1024111,"uid":75050,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"qwertyui<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e27589e817d60ac64f253229ae5c2867bf9da79","tid":1024111,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:05:51.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"cf18ece60592bfead6706738d7316f04989f2f42","tid":1024111,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"open source"},{"pid":"3a9db85bdcef137326af6d483c35b49e02e334b1","tid":1024111,"uid":169381,"like":121,"dislike":9,"score":112,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:09:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f36565b5e5eb1aa5ca0b9569a3d889c2435b4d51","tid":1024111,"uid":28563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"Tinker ❎<br />\nTinker<br />\n❎<br />\n@TinkerSec<br />\n&middot;<br />\n2月14日<br />\n~=8 Character Passwords Are Dead=~<br />\n<br />\nNew benchmark means that the entire keyspace, or every possible combination of:<br />\n- Upper<br />\n- Lower<br />\n- Number<br />\n- Symbol<br />\n<br />\n...of an 8 character password can be guessed in:<br />\n<br />\n~2.5 hours<br />\n<br />\n(8x 2080 GPUs against NTLM Windows hash)"},{"pid":"36b7e33d534e2366c8982ce4d2992922f3f883a6","tid":1024111,"uid":192732,"like":108,"dislike":6,"score":102,"quote":{"pid":"3a9db85bdcef137326af6d483c35b49e02e334b1","tid":1024111,"uid":169381,"like":121,"dislike":9,"score":112,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:09:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:16:58.000Z","msg":"其實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  比八位密碼安全"},{"pid":"aff647b7212ed2601f6a1eb41d0101588ecd751a","tid":1024111,"uid":60529,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:22:19.000Z","msg":"公司成日逼鳩人改埋d 大細階+數字+附號要10個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj